data.description: Beautifully remodeled Crescent model. New kitchen cabinets and countertops, gas cooktop, wall oven, stainless appliances. Lg laundry rm off kitchen with extra storage, extra lg garage with side door. Concrete floors throughout, den & office, remodeled primary bath with roll in shower, partially remodeled guest bath. Some roll down shades, French doors to a professionally landscaped yard and patio.
